Happy Magical Girl Monday!

While I didn’t complete the special attack code,  I still wanted to push a new build of the game. So I did!

There are still download keys available on Tumblr, so until they’re all gone, I will not be making The Magical Girl in PROXY a public download.

I’m going to continue working on the code throughout October, so expect more updates! I may make it a thing to push builds weekly, as long as there are no major errors. 
I’ve said it before, and I’m going to keep saying it until you’re all tired of hearing it:

If you haven’t, please read the first chapter of the light novel!

When you’ve finished, please let me know what you think! A lot of the conversations in the light novel are word for word what’s going to be in the cutscenes, so I want to make sure everything’s enjoyable, understandable, and without typos! 
Thank you for following the stories’/games’ development! If you like what you see, please like, reblog, comment, and share with your friends! Feedback is my greatest motivator!

Captain america and the avengers de super nintendo.
Un beat em up al estilo clasico de los años 90.
Aca controlamos a 4 vengadores para abrirnos pasos contra los enemigos,
Nuestros heroes son
Capitan america
Iron man
El androide vision
Y el tira flechas de Hawkeye
La historia nos cuenta como red skull o mas conocido como craneo rojo quiere conquistar el mundo.
Para lograr este cometido utiliza una maquina de control mental que la utiliza contra otros villanos, al tener control sobre estos villanos los utiliza para poder atacar ciudades y es en este momento cuando tomamos el control de nuestros heroes.
En fin....un juego de una calidad media que fue echo solo para fanaticos ya que no le llega ni a los talones a otros beat em up de la epoca tales como Final fight o capitan commando

Saludos 😘TAPIZA😘

A nossa vida é como uma roda gigante: uma hora estamos por cima, uma hora estamos por baixo. Em algum momento, algo ruim vai acontecer, acredite, nada é perfeito. Mas aí é que vem a lição e o aprendizado: se acontecer algo ruim, eu vou ser mais forte e aprender com aquilo! E logo após algo bom vai acontecer, é a lei da vida. Nada é ruim ou bom pra sempre.
As noite mais escuras, sempre serão clareadas pelo sol da manhã. Um lindo carrossel que encanta crianças, pode fazer parte de um filme de terror, quando desligado. 
A vida é isso. 
Ótima noite a todos.

caption.text: I dislike fighting BP

Mickey and Minnie set off on an adventure in search of a missing friend. On their journey they travel across many locations. Various stage themes consists of Pirates, Castles, and even a fun house. At the end of each act or location the duo encounters a Disney villain each from various franchises. When the duo finally finds there lost friend it is revealed to be Alice form Alice in Wonderland!

Very interesting note here is that the game was originally developed in japan on the famicom by HudsonSoft! When localized here in  the US many regional differences (assumably due to being published state side by capcom) in characters were either omitted or changed completely in the final cut. An Example of this is on the famicom the final boss you encounter is Cheshire Cat from Alice in wonderland and the US localization replaces the villain with Witch Hazel. Another instance is on Hooks ship on famicom you fight Captain Hook and on the IS version you fight peg Leg Pete. There are also rumors of a Hidden Mickey located somewhere on the rom board of the cartridge !

caption.text:
When I try on a cosplay, I film myself practicing poses and expressions to get into character and see what works for me and what doesn’t. Mostly I’m just thinking of as many quotes as I can and desperately wishing my voice sounded more like the character I’m cosplaying. 😂
Anyway, I had a lot of fun with this one and decided to splice it up and make a little Shulk video! My house is tiny so I didn’t have room to go all out with his attacks, but I’d like to run around outside sometime  and backslash to my heart’s content.
——

caption.text:
“Penalty of Justice”
Leverus is sent to the sentinel fort to investigate the aftermath of a siege. Upon arrival, there is no one to meet him. He then surveys the battlefield, which was completely desolated from the rampage that occurred. He investigated further, and spots what appears to be another person. Chasing after them, he finds that they disappeared... he then goes out to the balcony and is shoved off. As he thinks he’s about to die, he blacks out and wakes up near the forest. He then sees the mangled corpse of a fellow knight and decides to take action into his own hands and hunt down the samurai responsible.

caption.text:
September is Childhood Cancer Awareness Month 
We were purposely quiet for most of the month
Quietly we raised over $9500 during the month with events that spread awareness to golfers, gamers, local businesses and people that want to make a difference, that truly want to help kids cope with cancer.
With their help we are able upgrade gaming systems and extend our reach to more kids and families trying to cope and escape the reality of childhood cancer.

Did you know that they made a four player adapter for the NES? They actually made two! This is one of them - the NES Satellite. You just plug the little piece into the controller ports on the NES, plug four controllers into the big part, make sure you have six C batteries powering it, be playing one of the like five compatible games, and then you'll be rocking out four player style with hi-tech infrared technology!

There are only a handful of games that actually go with it. I think the only one I own that supports more than two players is MONOPOLY. Alternatively you can just use it as a wireless controller extension which was actually pretty cool in the late 80's when it came out.

This actually belongs to my good friend Mike, but I've been holding onto it indefinitely for him. He's always wanted to use it to play A Nightmare On Elm Street. One day that dream may still may become reality.

.⠀

.⠀
